flowchart TD
    Start([Development Workflow]) --> CodeChange[Developer Makes Code Change]
    CodeChange --> LocalUnit[Run Unit Tests Locally]
    LocalUnit --> UnitPass{Unit Tests Pass?}
    UnitPass -- Fail --> FixCode[Fix Failing Tests]
    FixCode --> CodeChange
    UnitPass -- Pass --> Commit[Commit Changes]
    Commit --> PreCommit[Pre-Commit Hook]
    PreCommit --> RunLint[Run Linters clang-format/clang-tidy]
    RunLint --> LintPass{Lint Pass?}
    LintPass -- Fail --> FixLint[Fix Lint Issues]
    FixLint --> Commit
    LintPass -- Pass --> RunInteg[Run Integration Tests]
    RunInteg --> IntegPass{Integration Pass?}
    IntegPass -- Fail --> FixInteg[Fix Integration Issues]
    FixInteg --> CodeChange
    IntegPass -- Pass --> Push[Push to Remote]
    Push --> CITrigger[CI Pipeline Triggered]
    CITrigger --> CIBuild[Build Project]
    CIBuild --> BuildOK{Build Success?}
    BuildOK -- Fail --> NotifyFail[Notify Developer]
    NotifyFail --> FixCode
    BuildOK -- Pass --> CIUnit[CI: Run Unit Tests]
    CIUnit --> CIInteg[CI: Run Integration Tests]
    CIInteg --> CIE2E[CI: Run E2E Tests]
    CIE2E --> AllPass{All Tests Pass?}
    AllPass -- Fail --> NotifyFail
    AllPass -- Pass --> Coverage[Generate Coverage Report]
    Coverage --> CoverageOK{Coverage â‰¥ 80%?}
    CoverageOK -- Fail --> NotifyLowCov[Notify Low Coverage]
    NotifyLowCov --> FixCode
    CoverageOK -- Pass --> Benchmark[Run Benchmarks]
    Benchmark --> PerfOK{Performance OK?}
    PerfOK -- Regression --> NotifyPerf[Notify Regression]
    NotifyPerf --> FixCode
    PerfOK -- Pass --> CISuccess[CI Success]
    CISuccess --> MergePR[Merge PR]
    MergePR --> End([Testing Complete])
